But really, as you've said yourself, you feel you were wrong. You can't ask that question and say yes. All I want is for everyone on the server to act with that level of respect, end of the day, if I miss 10 vindis in a row because we don't rush someone and they win, likely it will be our (insert major big mob here) that is protected by the same courtesy. <br>
<br>
After perusing the entire thread, (as I type this, I have another window open with the thread in it, so that I can reply to things as they come up and not try to remember everything as I go)<br>
<br>
I can close with saying just one thing. <br>
<br>
I agree with Jurrassic.<br>
<br>
yers,<br>
<br>
